         <abstract id="aspace_6574cba536dda50fae0061e34062c74d">Consists of letters to Peyre chiefly from French authors, plus one letter from Peyre to Donald Wing enclosing a typescript of Paul Claudel's "Partage de midi," which Peyre had made from the play at the Bibliotheque Nationale.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
